Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们需要天气预报{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're going to need weather reports...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是他们需要的是太空天气预报{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but they're going to be space weather reports.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们需要有卫星来监视太阳{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're going to need satellites monitoring the Sun...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们得到耀斑的预警{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}giving us advance warning of flares.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太阳发出的光只要8分钟就抵达月球了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The light from the Sun takes only eight minutes to reach the Moon.{\r}
