Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}致命的辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the lethal radiation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你会有几分钟 半个小时 争分夺秒{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You'd have minutes, half an hour, that sort of time frame...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}寻找庇护之地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}before you wanted to really be in a shelter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样的风暴可能会持续几天{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Such a storm might last for a couple of days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个保护办法就是居住在地下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One option for protection is living underground.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是别让荒芜的地形蒙骗了你{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But don't let the barren terrain fool you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}月球和火星依然是活跃的天体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Moon and Mars are still active bodies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}地球上能见到的自然灾害会时有发生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where natural disasters like those seen on Earth can strike.{\r}
