Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或火星的一个选择{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}on the Moon or on Mars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在月球或火星表面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On the surface of the Moon and Mars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}存在着太阳辐射 存在着宇宙辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}there's radiation from the Sun, there's cosmic radiation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}火星上 还有尘埃暴{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On Mars, there's dust storms.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我们呆在地下 可以避开那些危害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}lf we're underground, we're safe from those hazards...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是还有其它的危害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but we have other hazards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想象一下 在这个岩洞里 一旦发生地震{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Imagine being in this cave when there's quakes...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}岩石滚落 会砸中我们 压住我们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}rocks falling down, crushing us, pinning us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}月球或火星的星震{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A Moon or Marsquake...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同样会威胁到地面上的移民{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}could also threaten an aboveground colony.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}月球和火星没有板块{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Moon and Mars don't have tectonic plates...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}类似于引发地球大部分地震和火山{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}like the ones that cause most of Earth's quakes...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喷发的板块{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and volcanic eruptions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有活火山的迹象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And there are no signs of active volcanoes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是月球和火星同样有炙热的星核{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But the Moon and Mars do have hot cores.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以在热产生的对地表的压力作用下 就会产生震颤{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So as the pressure from that heat heads to the surface, the shaking starts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一旦发生星震 通常还会有另一个灾害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And where there's quakes, there's often another disaster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就在不久前 我们看到了火星上的山崩{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Just recently, we've seen a landslide occurring on Mars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是在轨摄像机所拍到的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It was captured with the cameras in orbit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此我们知道这个确实发生了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So we know this does happen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很难被发现{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that can be hard to predict.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们可以将基地建在某些地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We might put our base someplace...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里貌似万无一失{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}which appears perfectly safe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后 几年后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then, a few years later...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就会了解到存在着滑坡的危害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}realize that there's a landslide hazard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}科学家尚无法肯定200年发生在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Scientists are still unsure what started the 2008 landslide...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}火星北极附近的滑坡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}near the north pole of Mars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里是个冰冻的地区{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It was in an icy area...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}研究人员认为大部分滑坡物质是冰{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and researchers believe most of the slide material was ice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那类地形就是潜在的殖民地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's just the type of place a colony might be located...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以利用冰转变成饮用水{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to take advantage of converting the ice to drinkable water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使是遥远的星震也会触发殖民地周边的滑坡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Even a distant quake could still trigger a slide near a colony.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要是有条隐蔽的断层正好就在建筑下方有如何呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But what if a hidden fault line is running right under the buildings?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将来 空间移民定居月球或火星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the future, space colonists living on the Moon or Mars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将会面对大量的威胁{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}will have plenty of threats to deal with...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}包括月球和火星星震之类的自然灾害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}including natural disasters like moonquakes and Marsquakes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们的活跃程度不如我们所呆的地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're not active the way we're used to on Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们的活跃程度不同{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're active in different ways...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}程度有可能出人意料{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and there may be unexpected ways...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们有可能对我们造成问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that they could cause problems for us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}由于我们当前对这些世界的认识{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Since our current knowledge of these other worlds...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}实际上只是涉及了皮毛{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}has literally only scratched the surface...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有可能在将来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it's possible that in the future...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们有可能就在断层上建立基地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we could locate a base right over a fault line...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而没有意识到下面的情况{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}without realizing what's below.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为在携带东西上太空时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And since weight is always an issue...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}重量一直是个问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when carrying things into space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以较轻的建筑可能会相当脆弱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the lightweight buildings could be quite vulnerable...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尤其是外层{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}especially the outer layer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}万一保护层有什么意外{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}lf anything happens to that protective layer...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就会有麻烦 措手不及的麻烦{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that's trouble, very rapid trouble.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}由于空气流出定居点{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As the gases stream out of the habitat...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就必须有一个非常有效和快速的程序{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you've got to have a very efficient and quick procedure...{\r}
