Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}移民不可能选择{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's unlikely that colonists...{\r}
