Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.47,0:41:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你会患上幽闭恐惧症{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You can get claustrophobic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.60,0:41:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}隔壁的家伙已经搞得你神经兮兮{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The guy next door could really get on your nerves...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.85,0:41:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你某种程度想掐死他{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and you want to strangle him after a certain point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.48,0:41:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尽管事故并没有广泛宣传{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Although the incidents aren't highly publicized...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.07,0:41:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇航员间的相处在过去就存在着问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}crew members have had problems getting along in the past...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.24,0:41:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}结果相当危险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with dangerous results.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在1970年代 至少有一组苏联空间站的宇航员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There was at least one Soviet space station crew in the 1970s...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.08,0:41:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相处并不很融洽{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that didn't get along pretty famously...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.41,0:41:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}实际上据说发生了斗殴{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and actually supposedly had a fistfight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.67,0:41:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些压力将会在这些长时间的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}These stresses are going to manifest themselves...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.38,0:41:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}任务中自我表现出来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}on these long-duration missions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.88,0:41:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大家都认为它们不就是在自欺欺人{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Anybody who thinks they aren't is fooling himself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.38,0:41:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了让事情更加有趣{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And to make things even more interesting...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.43,0:42:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}俄国人据说在飞船上安排了枪支{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Russian cosmonauts supposedly have firearms stowed onboard...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.14,0:42:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是1965年偏离着陆点后 采取的一项预防措施{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as a precaution after an extremely off-course landing in 1965.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.56,0:42:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇航员降落在西伯利亚的森林里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The crew landed up in the woods in Siberia...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.32,0:42:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在那里呆了约三天时间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and were there for about three days...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.03,0:42:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们不得不击退狼群 直到自己被营救{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and they had to fight off wolves until they were rescued.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.16,0:42:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}经过了那项特使的使命后 苏联决定{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}After that particular mission, the Soviets decided...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.41,0:42:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们将在每一个联盟号太空舱里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that they were going to put a sawed-off shotgun...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.74,0:42:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}配置短筒猎枪{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in every Soyuz capsule...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.50,0:42:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以防类似的事情再次发生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in case something like that happened again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.33,0:42:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在据说宇航员都配有手枪{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The cosmonauts are now rumored to have handguns...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.25,0:42:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}存放在应急箱里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}stored in emergency kits.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.01,0:42:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是没有人急欲提供太空配枪的任何官方细节{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But no one is eager to offer any official details of guns in space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.34,0:42:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}配载武器所带来的风险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And the risk of having a weapon aboard...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.39,0:42:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一旦情绪失控 就难说了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}isn't just a concern if tempers flare.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.18,0:42:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}实际上有一个实验任务专家的备案案例{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There is actually a documented case...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.77,0:42:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他曾经搭载过航天飞机{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of a payload specialist, who flew on a shuttle flight...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.82,0:42:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们的实验失败了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}whose experiment failed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.53,0:43:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他毕生都在为这个实验做准备{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and he spent his whole life getting this experiment ready...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.07,0:43:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}实验失败后 他真的考虑过自杀{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it failed, and he actually talked about killing himself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.87,0:43:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}组员们其实试图保护他{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And the crew themselves actually tried to protect him...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.29,0:43:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}守住舱口 这样他就没办法将他们杀死{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and guarded the hatch so he wouldn't kill them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.38,0:43:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}纵然得到了迄今为止所有太空旅行的经验教训{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Even with all of the space travel lessons learned so far...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.26,0:43:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一点是明白无误的:{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}one thing is clear:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.05,0:43:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谁都无法阻止{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}nothing can completely prevent disasters...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.64,0:43:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将来所遭遇的灾难{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from striking in the future.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.06,0:43:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我们要继续人类太空飞行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If we're going to continue human space flight...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.06,0:43:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们就必须接受这种风险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we have to accept the risk...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.40,0:43:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为这是个非常危险的活动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because it is a very dangerous occupation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.02,0:43:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是我们必须应对风险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But we have to manage the risk...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.61,0:43:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那将需要出色的技术人员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that's going to require good technical people...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.15,0:43:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}和出色的领导{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and good leadership.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.99,0:43:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是正如灾难不可避免一样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But just as surely as disasters will strike...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.95,0:43:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}另外一点也是必然的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}there is another certainty...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.29,0:43:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要提及载人航天探索{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when it comes to manned space exploration.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.42,0:43:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我认为我们有一个基因{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I think we have a gene...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}探索的基因{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a gene for exploration...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.09,0:43:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}发现的基因{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a gene for discovery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.47,0:44:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不仅仅是它有益于我们的进化{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Not only is it good for our evolution...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.72,0:44:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我们找到了繁育和殖民的新途径{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because we find new avenues to reproduce and to colonize...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.68,0:44:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同时我认为在我们人类的灵魂深处{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but I think it's also inside the spirit of human beings...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.14,0:44:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是想了解外面的世界{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to want to know what's out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.77,0:44:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是否有可能到达我们以前从未涉足过的地方呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Is it possible to reach areas that we've never been before?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.56,0:44:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}刺激...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And the thrill...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.77,0:44:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}作为探索新大陆第一人的刺激{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the thrill of being the first person to explore new terrain...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.17,0:44:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}实在是妙不可言{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is simply fantastic.{\r}
